fields.name: Ring
fields.description:
The Avery Hammered Gold Ring by CaratLane is a beautiful and simple piece of jewellery that is perfect for everyday wear. Made with 18kt yellow gold, the ring features a hammered texture that adds a unique and stylish touch to the overall design. The ring also offers the option for personalized engraving, making it a thoughtful and meaningful gift for a loved one or as a special addition to your own jewellery collection. The simple and sober design of the Avery Hammered Gold Ring makes it a versatile choice for any occasion.
Every design has a unique character and texture as each one is uniquely handcrafted with the traditional hammer technique
